    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model is acceptable for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. Despite discretization error, output comparison, and model inputs factors not reaching their required levels, the team judged the overall body of evidence sufficient given the conservative nature of the hemolysis power-law model and the use of the FDA benchmark dataset. The relative hemolysis index remains below 1.0 across all operating points. The decision is Accepted at Medium assurance.",
